data.title: Electronic Line-calling Malfunction Costs Ljubicic at Indian Wells Tennis
meta_keywords: Electronic Line-calling Malfunction Costs Ljubicic at Indian Wells Tennis
data.meta_description: After losing the replay point, Ljubicic lost the next point to lose his serve, walking to his chair for the changeover while the Indian Wells crowd booed the electronic line call.
